{"tid":2067594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Now新聞台】譚耀宗：中央有權要求疑犯移送內地受審","createTime":"2020-06-17T06:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T06:39:10.000Z","uid":37554,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b76b539fb4a499d9972fbf2c5b4d004a318aa6d5","tid":2067594,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】人大常委譚耀宗指，未獲通知周四召開的常委會會審議港區國安法，但相信會加緊立法程序。他又指，不能排除中央有權要求將觸犯港區國安法的人移送內地受審。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會周四召開例會，將會到開會的人大常委譚耀宗指，至今議程未提及會審議港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦副主任鄧中華日前指，中央會保留極為特殊、嚴重案件的執法、司法管轄權。譚耀宗認為，外國勢力干預香港事務，涉及外交事務和國家行為，明顯應由中央處理，至於是否代表違反港區國安法的人要到內地受審，譚耀宗指不排除這個選項。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗又指，不了解日後內地駐港國安人員能否合法持械。他認為，若中央在香港設立國安機構，會與港府相應機構協調，主要擔任指導角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394760&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=d6cb6f4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394760&h=82c4ac6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=394760</a>"},{"pid":"2147bc4678a63d4a9308b3c8bfecd23e11ab3702","tid":2067594,"uid":40499,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"第一個送你宗"},{"pid":"609920680e195221e8033b312ad5e3daa3530475","tid":2067594,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"又想送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6869d8d054fba88d5f39d331c1cfc5e197a869b9","tid":2067594,"uid":124277,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"